title: Murder on the High Seas aka Love Bound (1932) Drama, Mystery Movie

sources.title: Murder on the High Seas aka Love Bound (1932) Drama, Mystery Movie
sources.description:
A gold-digging woman wins a big settlement against an older married man, which threatens to destroy the man's family. His son, discovers that the woman is part of a ring of blackmailers.
 
Director: Robert F. Hill
Writers: James R. Gilbert, Robert F. Hill 
Stars: Jack Mulhall, Natalie Moorhead, Clara Kimball Young 
Genres: Classics, Drama, Mystery
